INSHORE WATERS FORECAST TO 12 MILES OFFSHORE FOR THE PERIOD 0000 UTC MONDAY
13 DECEMBER TO 0000 UTC TUESDAY 14 DECEMBER 2021
GENERAL SITUATION
A DEEP AREA OF LOW PRESSURE WILL PASS NORTH-EASTWARDS CLOSE TO THE NORTHWEST
CORNER OF SCOTLAND ON SUNDAY NIGHT. THIS WILL BRING A SPELL STORM FORCE WINDS
TO SOME NORTHWESTERN WATERS AND GALES FOR MANY NORTHERN AND WESTERN AREAS.
